SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from ordersdetaillering d, rekeningen_per_product r, producten p, od_prod_ordstat s where d.orx_ordernummer = ~1 and d.orx_orderregel = ~2 and d.orx_relatie = r.rpp_relatienummer and d.orx_geldrekening = r.rpp_rekening_nummer and d.orx_geldrekreksoort = r.rpp_rekeningsoort and d.orx_geldrekvaluta = r.rpp_valuta and r.rpp_productnummer = p.pr_productnummer and p.pr_id = s.pr_id and s.stst_internalnr = ~3
select w.id from order_initiation o inner join order_lines l on to_char(l.order_reference) = o.orin_reference inner join wm_order w on w.id = l.wm_order_id where o.orin_id = ~1
